title: Alien Encounters 004 ( Re Edit) ( Carbunkle DCP)
description: Alien Encounters is an American science fiction anthology comic book published by FantaCo Enterprises and then Eclipse Comics . The comic debuted with FantaCo in 1981, and in 1985 was revived by Eclipse, where (starting over from issue 1) it ran for fourteen issues until 1987. Eclipse began publishing the title soon after the cancellation of Alien Worlds , a similar science-fiction themed anthology.
